    • deParseReferentialActions

      private String deParseReferentialActions(net.sf.jsqlparser.statement.create.table.ForeignKeyIndex index)
      Returns ForeignKeyIndex as RegEx.. Mimicking toString method of index superclass and subtracts it from the ForeignKeyIndex toString string. With that its possible to deParse: "CONSTRAINT symbol FOREIGN KEY (col1) REFERENCES table2 (col1, col2) MATCH FULL" with maximum variance in whiteSpaces.
      Parameters:
      index - ForeignKeyIndex
      Returns:
      ForeignKeyIndex as RegEx
